<a name="quick"></a> <a name="pc-pine">&nbsp;</a> 
<h1>
Quick Start 
</h1>

<div class="bod"> 
  <table width="90%" bgcolor="#ffff80" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tbody><tr valign="top"> 
      <td><b><i><font size="+1">Note</font></i></b></td>
      <td>&nbsp; &nbsp;</td>
      <td>Some service providers, for example <a href="http://www.cyberspace.org/faq.html#fromhdr">Grex</a>, 
          have set up their installation of Pine so that users cannot change 
          their From&nbsp;header.</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody></table>
  
  <table align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="50">
    <tbody><tr> 
      <td class="solidborder" align="center" bgcolor="#ffffff" nowrap="nowrap"><p class="headfoot">&nbsp;<a href="http://www.ii.com/#supportii">S<small>UPPORT</small> I<small>NFINITE</small> 
          I<small>NK!</small></a>&nbsp;</p></td>
    </tr>
    <tr> 
